{"Sid":0,"Did":118197,"Id":"282410","Title":"羅東城隍廟重建寄附碑","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collection/c6ec929b-bc5c-437e-aa89-f2e5671aad27/108-her-pa-1971-201911011836325dbc0a54652f10.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collection/626a4497-e2f7-49d6-b9b3-bbc2c9082258/108-her-pa-1971-201911011836325dbc0a54652f11.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n羅東城隍廟在1933（日昭和8）年重建時，地方居民都踴躍寄附，廟方將寄附者的姓名與寄附金額都以寄附碑方式嵌在城隍廟步口廊對看牆上。寄附金額較高者，都是當時地方領導階級，如寄附金額最高者為林嘉普醫師，為時任羅東街長陳純精之女婿，其診所即在城隍廟旁。至於亦曾在羅東奠安宮與震安宮重建時寄附甚多的地方頭人，如林燦然、胡慶森、張新納、張阿力、朱粗皮等人亦皆寄附一定金額。在虎邊寄附碑，標示了發起人陳純精、范純喜、陳東山、廖錫泉、張添木與張文章；寄附碑另一側，則標示了羅東城隍廟竣工時間是在「昭和八年歲次癸酉冬季」。此兩方寄附碑都是由宜蘭街的手繪彩磁店家「新永昌」所製作。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7715338","Keyword_Latitude":"24.6759883","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/6D4D4765-35E0-4C24-B3D3-173961086930","Original_Identifier":"282410","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"寄附 / 陳純精 / 新永昌 / 羅東城隍廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:33:56","timelines":"","place":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮中正路128號","address":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮中正路128號","longitude":"121.7715338","latitude":"24.6759883","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collectionOpen/2afd9d97-8bfb-4df9-9b6e-fbbb7c74b0d0/108-her-pa-1971-re-201911011839185dbc0a54652f10.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collectionOpen/4839b54a-b8b8-4d62-b377-7d7ba716ae27/108-her-pa-1971-re-201911011839185dbc0a54652f